cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL. 

The paper deals with the task of generating abstractive snippets, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval. Therefore, cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.LG (Learning) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a new approach to abstractive snippet generation using machine learning techniques, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DL (Deep Learning).
